you're saying.

26:05.731 --> 26:07.566 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DR. DELANEY RUSTON: Absolutely.

26:07.666 --> 26:12.971 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
