27:10.863 --> 27:15.267 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: I mean, does
that kind of
stuff terrify you? Or do you
think this research

27:15.367 --> 27:19.071 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
