mean, how
are people supposed to process
this information?

27:19.171 --> 27:23.876 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. DELANEY RUSTON: You know, I
think it's
a question about how much we're
giving kids

27:23.976 --> 27:29.648 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
full potential in everything
that they do.
And, to me, a big issue is how
much time they

27:29.748 --> 27:35.988 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
have with all sorts of skills
