we're at that place yet where we
need to be

27:59.077 --> 28:00.913 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
really alarmist.

28:01.013 --> 28:04.116 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Let's say I'm
a parent and
I come to you and I say, I have
a young kid,

28:04.216 --> 28:08.453 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
maybe a 10-year-old daughter.
