I get her a phone? What would
you tell this

28:08.554 --> 28:10.355 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
parent?

28:10.455 --> 28:13.592 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. DELANEY RUSTON: I think, you
