and younger. And when we bring
them -- start

28:23.135 --> 28:27.239 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
having them in elementary
school, we have
to wonder, when is it too young
that they're

28:27.339 --> 28:32.477 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
not going to be able to resist
the impulse
to check or to post?

28:32.578 --> 28:36.615 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN: Every girl in the picture
is locked into
her phone. Peralta knocks it
into center.

28:36.715 --> 28:44.222 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
David tonight 2-2, a leadoff
