28:44.323 --> 28:48.060 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We need to -- can we do an
intervention?

28:48.160 --> 28:54.399 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. DELANEY RUSTON: This is all
about teaching
kids self-control, and what we
have learned

28:54.499 --> 29:00.238 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
through the research is that
