teachable. So, I would really
discourage a

29:00.339 --> 29:05.777 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
family from getting a child a
device when
they don't feel like they are
going to be

29:05.877 --> 29:09.781 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
able to control themselves from
when they
use it.

29:09.881 --> 29:15.887 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Ruston has
been taking her
film across the country
recently, holding

29:15.988 --> 29:21.760 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
screenings in dozens of cities,
