45:22.153 --> 45:23.988 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMES MCBRIDE, Author, "Kill 'Em
and Leave:
Searching for James Brown and
the American

45:24.088 --> 45:27.124 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Soul": Well, there's no music in
