shook America
up, and James Brown shook the
world up, because

45:41.472 --> 45:49.413 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
his whole persona was that of
someone whose
consumed by this music, this
sound.

45:49.513 --> 45:54.051 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, he was a phenomena. And he
was really
seen as a kind of a scream at
