46:39.630 --> 46:42.333 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMES MCBRIDE: Well, everything
about the
way he lived, everything about
his lifestyle

46:42.433 --> 46:48.439 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
