integrity of Southern
life.

46:52.677 --> 46:57.815 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, you know the whole business
of him doing
his hair, for example, and
always being proper,

46:57.915 --> 47:03.187 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
