whole business
of trust in the South, and
especially in James

47:03.287 --> 47:08.793 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Brown's world, and you talk to
Southerners,
this -- this whole mentality of,
if we trust

47:08.893 --> 47:14.498 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
