life, but
if you betray that trust, our
journey is over.

47:14.598 --> 47:24.809 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And James Brown really typified
that in many
ways.

47:24.909 --> 47:35.419 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: But you also talk
about the
idea of putting on a face,
