a very lonely
and fearful person.

48:08.886 --> 48:13.624 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But he never showed that to
people. His face
was that of bravado and pride
and smiling.

48:13.724 --> 48:19.196 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
