didn't want
people to know him.

48:19.296 --> 48:33.043 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes, that comes
through. Right?
I mean, he's a very hard man to
know, even

48:33.144 --> 48:35.112 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
