very close
to him.

48:35.212 --> 48:38.349 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JAMES MCBRIDE: Well, you know,
he compartmentalized
people.

48:38.449 --> 48:41.419 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You know, he had his black
friends. He had
his white friends. He had his
manager that

48:41.519 --> 48:44.021 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
