his accountant
that he trusted with his money.
And he had

48:44.121 --> 48:46.791 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
this promoter that he trusted
and that one
he didn't.

48:46.891 --> 48:54.231 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He lived in a world of many
rooms. I don't
know if he is that different
from any of us.

48:54.331 --> 49:00.304 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But he is an exaggeration of all
of us, because
he doesn't know how to quite
function comfortably

49:00.404 --> 49:02.239 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in any one place.

49:02.339 --> 49:06.210 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And what about
the way he was
treated, seen? I mean, you are
talking about

49:06.310 --> 49:10.881 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
