much more

49:10.981 --> 49:11.549 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
attention.

49:11.649 --> 49:13.450 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JAMES MCBRIDE: Of course.

49:13.551 --> 49:17.588 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Well, I mean, listen, the whole
business of
the evolution of black music in
America is

49:17.688 --> 49:22.293 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
