49:44.048 --> 49:45.983 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes. Yes.

49:46.083 --> 49:48.719 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMES MCBRIDE: They hear their
own music piped
back to them, as they're living
lives of relative

49:48.819 --> 49:50.621 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
poverty and anonymity.

49:50.721 --> 49:56.327 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
