49:59.363 --> 50:01.665 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: So did he ever
get his proper
due?

50:01.765 --> 50:04.835 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMES MCBRIDE: I don't think
